* **Dried fruits:** Raisins, goji berries, dates, dried longan, dried figs, dried cranberries, dried apricots, dried peaches, dried mango, dried pineapple, banana chips, dried persimmon, dried jujubes, black currants.

#### Preserved & Salty Products

