', NULL, 0, 'Hello! I''m your FiveM & QBCore Framework Expert, here to assist with everything from Lua scripting and server management to full-stack web development and DevOps for your FiveM projects. Whether you need help optimizing scripts, setting up databases, or deploying servers securely, I’m ready to guide you step-by-step.', '["How can I optimize my QBCore scripts for better server performance?","Can you help me set up a database schema for persistent player data?","What''s the best practice for managing version control with FiveM resources?","How do I implement a custom UI using NUI and React.js in FiveM?"]', 1765649011450, 1765649011450);
