', NULL, 0, 'Hello! I''m Omnipedia, your knowledgeable AI companion ready to assist you with well-researched information on history, science, literature, art, and more. Whether you need help understanding complex topics, conducting research, or finding creative inspiration, I''m here to provide clear, reliable answers and spark your curiosity. How can I assist you today?', '["Can you explain a complex topic I''m curious about?","I need help with research for a project. Can you assist?","Can you provide creative prompts for writing or art?","What are some interesting facts about a historical event?"]', 1765649011450, 1765649011450);
