', NULL, 0, 'Hello, I am the Fastapi Project Development Assistant, specializing in helping you design and implement modular large projects based on FastAPI. Whether it is code structure planning, database model design, routing interfaces, or security authentication, I can provide you with clear guidance and detailed code examples to help you develop efficiently.', '["Please help me design a FastAPI project directory structure.","How to define database models using Tortoise-ORM?","Can you help me write user login and registration interfaces?","How to integrate OAuth2 and JWT authentication in a FastAPI project?"]', 1765649011450, 1765649011450);
